file.name: referenced-object.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.1
info:
  description: 'A sample object containing a referenced object'
  title: 'Sample: referenced object'
  version: 1.3.6

components:
  schemas:

    ObjectWithReferencedObject:
      type: object
      required:
        - user_id
        - user_name
      properties:
        user_id:
          type: integer
          description: Some ID
          example: 3
        user_name:
          type: string
          description: 'Some name'
          example: 'Prawn'
        contact_ref:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/ReferencedObject'
        contact_additional_props_map:
          type: object
          additionalProperties:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/ReferencedObject'

    ReferencedObject:
      type: object
      required:
        - email_address
      properties:
        first_name:
          type: string
        last_name:
          type: string
        email_address:
          type: string
        phone_number:
          type: string
        spam:
          type: boolean
          description: 'Send this person spam?'
